    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TetriMatch is a fresh new take on Tetris incorporating Match 3 game mechanics to add a extra layer of challenge to a classic. The player will have powerups at their disposal to help clear out blocks if things get to hectic. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenges the player will face will range from increased fall speed of blocks to blocks turning to stone after a period of time. These will have to be overcome as the player tries to get a high score and survive the ever increasing difficulty! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mouse and Keyboard controls</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click and drag to move individual blocks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click powerup and click on level to use it</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WASD &amp; Arrow Keys to move and place block shapes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >W &amp; Up Arrow key to rotate block shapes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Space Bar to save a block shape for later or use the saved block shape</p></li></ul>",
